    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">âœ… OpenShift Deployment Success</div>
        <p>Dear Team,</p>
        <p>The OpenShift deployment has been successfully completed.</p>
        <p><strong>Environment:</strong> INT</p>
        <p><strong>Timestamp:</strong> $(date)</p>
        <p>For more details, check the logs in OpenShift.</p>
        <div class="footer">This is an automated notification from OpenShift.</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
EOF
)

